Package: shinytest2assist
Title: MCP Server for Generating Shinytest2 Test Cases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An MCP (Model Context Protocol) server that generates automated test cases 
    for shiny applications using shinytest2. It converts natural language prompts 
    into executable test code using advanced NLP parsing and browser automation.
